				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think the biggest difference between the two games since they are alot alike.... is the item gathering and xp in WOW
<br />

<br />
There are so many way to get items: 
<br />
you can quest and usually choose your reward, 
<br />
you can fish and come up with a chest full of loot or a rare pearl,
<br />
you can find these "mini dungeons" or caves to go kill many monsters in very few minutes
<br />
you can swim underwater or hunt around mobs and find treasure chests
<br />

<br />
AND 
<br />

<br />
if you dont want to continually grind thru levels every day you can get good xp from quests and if you log out at the Inn, the longer you are away the more xp you get when you get back...so its an edge for those that can only play a few times a week we can finally keep up with the ones that pay 24-7.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
